nodes.text: This unidentified Ithorian lived in the Galactic City of Coruscant and worked as a musician along with three Bith in a cantina. Around 21 BBY, when bounty hunters Robonino and Chata Hyoki came to the cantina to discuss their plan to assassinate senator Padmé Amidala with Count Dooku, this Ithorian was playing a flute-like instrument.
